name: FGameplayCueNotify_SpawnResult
doc:
FGameplayCueNotify_SpawnResult

    Temporary structure used to track results of spawning components.

FxSystemComponents: List of FX components spawned.  There may be null pointers here as it matches the defined order.
AudioComponents: List of audio components spawned.  There may be null pointers here as it matches the defined order.
CameraShakes: List of camera shakes played.  There will be one camera shake per local player controller if shake is played in world.
ForceFeedbackComponent: Force feedback component that was spawned.  This is only valid when force feedback is set to play in world.
DecalComponent: Spawned decal component.  This may be null.
